1
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:12,167
<i> I love you so much.</i>

2
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:13,667
<i> Oh, really?</i>

3
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:16,533
<i>I will do anything for you,
Dear.</i>

4
00:00:16,667 --> 00:00:17,967
<i> Talk to Emma.</i>

5
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:21,533
<i>Tell her to drop all charges
against me.</i>

6
00:00:21,667 --> 00:00:23,567
<i> Please, Emma, do it for me.</i>

7
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:26,267
<i>I can't forgive her
for what she did to my daughter.</i>

8
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:29,333
<i>I'm sorry, but you'll never see
me defeated.</i>

9
00:00:29,467 --> 00:00:31,133
<i> You made Mookie suffer!</i>

10
00:00:31,267 --> 00:00:34,067
<i>That's why I can never forgive
you.</i>

11
00:00:34,233 --> 00:00:35,600
<i> You can rot in jail!</i>

12
00:00:35,733 --> 00:00:36,667
<i> Get out of here!</i>

13
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:39,867
<i>My mom is hoping that Olive will
accept her.</i>

14
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,200
<i> But Olive is just using her.</i>

15
00:00:41,333 --> 00:00:43,700
<i>Astrid told me
about your condition.</i>

16
00:00:43,833 --> 00:00:47,200
<i>Your Munchausen syndrome
by proxy or MSBP.</i>

17
00:01:25,267 --> 00:01:29,267
Go on! Come on!
Try to come near me!

18
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,233
I will blow her head up!

19
00:01:31,367 --> 00:01:32,067
Olive!

20
00:01:34,033 --> 00:01:35,833
Olive, I'm the only ally you
have left.

21
00:01:35,967 --> 00:01:37,667
Everyone turned their back
on you.

22
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:40,200
Olive, please.
Why are you doing this?

23
00:01:40,333 --> 00:01:41,733
I don't care!

24
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:44,533
Don't come near me!

25
00:01:44,667 --> 00:01:46,633
Or else I will blow her head up!

26
00:01:46,767 --> 00:01:48,467
Olive, I'm your friend.
Have you forgotten that?

27
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,900
I don't give damn!

28
00:01:50,033 --> 00:01:51,500
Don't come near me!

29
00:01:51,633 --> 00:01:53,200
Don't you dare!

30
00:01:53,333 --> 00:01:56,067
If you cooperate with me,
you won't get hurt.

31
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,000
Olive, please.

32
00:01:57,133 --> 00:01:58,667
I just need to get out of here,
Astrid.

33
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:00,533
What are you thinking?

34
00:02:00,667 --> 00:02:01,467
How can you do that
to your friend?

35
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,533
Don't come near me!

36
00:02:02,667 --> 00:02:03,867
Don't you dare!

37
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,433
I will shoot her in the head!

38
00:02:06,567 --> 00:02:07,733
Listen to her!

39
00:02:07,867 --> 00:02:11,033
Please, or she'll shoot me!

40
00:02:11,167 --> 00:02:12,267
Olive!

41
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:15,533
Olive, Dear. Please don't
do that! Put the gun down!

42
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:16,700
Olive.

43
00:02:16,833 --> 00:02:17,633
Olive, please.

44
00:02:17,767 --> 00:02:20,233
I know her well,
she will shoot me.

45
00:02:25,567 --> 00:02:28,433
Mom, no. I'll talk to her!

46
00:02:28,567 --> 00:02:29,367
Olive!

47
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:31,600
- Mom!
- Mom.

48
00:02:33,833 --> 00:02:35,400
My mom might get hurt.

49
00:02:35,533 --> 00:02:36,433
- Come on.
- Emma.

50
00:02:36,567 --> 00:02:38,067
Let's follow them.

51
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:46,000
Give me your keys!

52
00:02:46,133 --> 00:02:46,867
Move!

53
00:02:53,133 --> 00:02:53,967
What the heck!

54
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:58,300
Olive!

55
00:02:59,333 --> 00:02:59,933
Olive!

56
00:03:01,733 --> 00:03:03,167
Stop! Stop!

57
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,667
Jade!

58
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,300
What did you do to your sister?

59
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,300
You're always meddling
with my plans! Move!

60
00:03:10,433 --> 00:03:11,567
I'm begging you.

61
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:13,167
Don't hurt your sister.

62
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:14,900
Don't hurt Jade.

63
00:03:19,133 --> 00:03:21,033
Jade! Sweetie!
Wake up! Olive!

64
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,200
Grandmother!

65
00:03:22,333 --> 00:03:23,400
Grandmother!

66
00:03:23,533 --> 00:03:24,500
- Mookie.
- Mom.

67
00:03:24,633 --> 00:03:25,900
Follow Olive!

68
00:03:26,033 --> 00:03:27,100
Jade is unconscious!

69
00:03:27,233 --> 00:03:31,367
We have to follow them. Come on!
Olive might hurt Jade!

70
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:33,033
Let's go. Follow her!

71
00:03:33,967 --> 00:03:35,767
You will never catch me alive!

72
00:03:42,233 --> 00:03:46,667
If I'm going to die,
you are coming with me.

73
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,833
Because you're a meddler!

74
00:03:49,967 --> 00:03:50,967
A traitor!

75
00:03:52,167 --> 00:03:57,933
Oh well, we're twins, right?

76
00:03:59,067 --> 00:04:03,500
We're connected.

77
00:04:04,933 --> 00:04:09,800
We will die together!

78
00:04:15,533 --> 00:04:18,367
She might hurt Jade.

79
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:20,967
- What are we gonna do now?
- You guys should stay here.

80
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:22,033
I'm coming with you.

81
00:04:22,167 --> 00:04:24,033
You can't, you might get hurt.

82
00:04:25,067 --> 00:04:28,467
We should stay here.
Let him do the chasing.

83
00:04:28,633 --> 00:04:30,233
Mom, we'll be careful.

84
00:04:30,367 --> 00:04:31,400
But...

85
00:04:31,533 --> 00:04:34,367
Go on then, we'll take care
of Ligaya and Mookie.

86
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,633
Don't go too close to Olive.

87
00:04:36,767 --> 00:04:38,800
That woman lost her mind.

88
00:04:39,967 --> 00:04:42,433
I'm sure the police officers
will not stop chasing me.

89
00:04:43,933 --> 00:04:45,200
Emma too!

90
00:04:45,333 --> 00:04:46,967
No!

91
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:50,567
I won't let them catch me!
You can't catch me!

92
00:04:53,333 --> 00:04:55,900
I'm not going back to jail.

93
00:04:56,033 --> 00:04:57,467
No!

94
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,267
I can't let that happen.

95
00:05:01,367 --> 00:05:03,833
Stay here, sweetie.

96
00:05:03,967 --> 00:05:05,967
We'll find Olive and Jade.

97
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:09,667
Be careful, Mom and Dad.

98
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:12,333
Don't worry about us.

99
00:05:12,467 --> 00:05:15,633
Go on ahead! Stop talking!
You should go right now!

100
00:05:15,767 --> 00:05:18,200
- Come on, let's go.
- Hurry up!

101
00:05:18,333 --> 00:05:21,667
- Keep us updated.
- Mookie.

102
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,367
Be careful.

103
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,867
What's happening?

104
00:05:43,933 --> 00:05:45,867
Why did it stop?

105
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,400
No!

106
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,967
What the heck,
why did it stop now?

107
00:06:01,167 --> 00:06:02,433
No!

108
00:06:05,367 --> 00:06:06,500
No.

109
00:06:06,633 --> 00:06:08,333
What am I going to do?

110
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,767
Where can I go?

111
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:11,033
Come on, Olive.

112
00:06:11,167 --> 00:06:12,700
Think, Think.

113
00:06:12,833 --> 00:06:15,267
Think of a way.

114
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,700
What am I going to do?

115
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:17,800
What do I do?

116
00:06:17,933 --> 00:06:19,267
How can I escape?

117
00:06:21,333 --> 00:06:22,567
Come on, Olive.

118
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:23,467
Think!

119
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,367
Think!

120
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,100
Jade?

121
00:06:29,767 --> 00:06:30,567
Jade!

122
00:06:31,967 --> 00:06:32,833
Jade!

123
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,400
Where are you going?
I'm not done with you!

124
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,033
That's the car Olive and Jade
were in.

125
00:06:43,267 --> 00:06:45,000
Looks like the car broke down.

126
00:06:45,133 --> 00:06:46,467
Come on, let's check it out.

127
00:07:01,233 --> 00:07:02,900
I'll check the backside.

128
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:06,967
They're not here.

129
00:07:09,133 --> 00:07:12,867
At first, I thought Jade
was working with Olive.

130
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,967
But when we spent time with her,

131
00:07:15,133 --> 00:07:17,733
I felt she was different from
Olive.

132
00:07:18,833 --> 00:07:20,633
I hope nothing bad happens
to Jade.

133
00:07:21,667 --> 00:07:25,367
Let's consider that Jade
is still Olive's sister.

134
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:27,000
I hope Olive will consider that.

135
00:07:27,133 --> 00:07:29,900
I don't know what she's
thinking.

136
00:07:30,033 --> 00:07:31,800
Olive, please!

137
00:07:31,933 --> 00:07:33,933
Let's stop this.

138
00:07:34,867 --> 00:07:37,567
Olive, stop!

139
00:07:44,667 --> 00:07:46,133
Olive, stop!

140
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:50,000
The law will chase you down
no matter where you go.

141
00:07:51,067 --> 00:07:54,367
They won't stop until
they put you back in jail.

142
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,500
I don't give a damn!

143
00:07:56,633 --> 00:07:58,267
Olive, please.

144
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,900
Let's stop this.

145
00:08:01,033 --> 00:08:02,967
What is going on with you?

146
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:06,300
I'm your sister!

147
00:08:06,433 --> 00:08:07,833
We grew up together.

148
00:08:07,967 --> 00:08:09,933
We've been through
a lot together.

149
00:08:10,067 --> 00:08:12,267
Why are you doing this to me?

150
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:15,000
Why did you think
of that just now?

151
00:08:15,133 --> 00:08:17,300
We grew up together, right?

152
00:08:17,433 --> 00:08:19,133
We should have each other's
backs.

153
00:08:19,267 --> 00:08:21,300
But what did you do?

154
00:08:21,467 --> 00:08:24,300
You took Emma's side!

155
00:08:24,433 --> 00:08:25,900
Olive.

156
00:08:26,033 --> 00:08:29,067
Please open your heart.

157
00:08:30,533 --> 00:08:33,133
Give them a chance!

158
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:40,200
Dan, they're not here.

159
00:08:40,333 --> 00:08:42,367
They probably went over there.

160
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:43,367
Come on, let's go.

161
00:08:54,867 --> 00:08:59,000
I know how hard it is
for Ligaya to give us up.

162
00:09:02,333 --> 00:09:07,967
But she has to do it to give us
a better life.

163
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:13,333
She chose to give us up,
so we won't suffer.

164
00:09:14,633 --> 00:09:18,600
She chose to give us
a better life, Olive.

165
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,933
You've been a mother, too.

166
00:09:23,367 --> 00:09:27,733
You know how hard it
is to lose a child.

167
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:32,600
Especially now that you lost
Mookie.

168
00:09:32,733 --> 00:09:37,933
It will be easier
if you surrender.

169
00:09:39,733 --> 00:09:45,300
And I promise that we will
support you.

170
00:09:46,767 --> 00:09:51,600
We will be there for you,
we have a family now.

171
00:09:51,733 --> 00:09:56,233
We will never be alone.
We have a mother now.

172
00:09:56,367 --> 00:09:59,900
Our mom will be there for us
now.

173
00:10:03,833 --> 00:10:06,467
Don't worry too much,
Grandmother.

174
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:14,567
I'm sure they'll be okay.
Everything will be okay.

175
00:10:14,700 --> 00:10:15,867
- I hope so.
- Don't worry.

176
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,933
I hope they're okay.

177
00:10:20,667 --> 00:10:23,333
I hope they'll get along.

178
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:28,400
Nothing else can make me happy

179
00:10:28,533 --> 00:10:31,967
but seeing my children get
along.

180
00:10:32,100 --> 00:10:33,433
Shut up!

181
00:10:33,567 --> 00:10:37,033
If you don't, I'll hit you!

182
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,633
Please, Olive.

183
00:10:38,767 --> 00:10:39,600
Please.

184
00:10:40,733 --> 00:10:43,100
Please, stop this.

185
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:47,567
A lot of people love you.
We're here for you.

186
00:10:47,700 --> 00:10:49,633
We love you.

187
00:10:49,767 --> 00:10:52,333
Please stop this now.
Please stop.

188
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:55,900
I don't need anyone else
but Mookie!

189
00:10:56,033 --> 00:10:58,600
Mookie is the only family
I have!

190
00:10:58,733 --> 00:11:05,067
But because of you and Emma,
I lost my daughter!

191
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:12,133
You're too much!

192
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,967
Let go!

193
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:19,367
You have nothing!

194
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:22,400
You have no achievements
like I do!

195
00:11:22,533 --> 00:11:24,767
Fine, you have achievements!

196
00:11:24,900 --> 00:11:28,000
But even if I didn't listen
to Mom and Dad,

197
00:11:28,133 --> 00:11:30,100
the choices I made,
made me happy.

198
00:11:30,233 --> 00:11:31,333
What about you?

199
00:11:31,467 --> 00:11:33,133
Are you happy?

200
00:11:33,267 --> 00:11:36,233
Your heart is filled with
hatred and resentment.

201
00:11:36,367 --> 00:11:38,367
And look at what you've become!

202
00:11:50,700 --> 00:11:51,433
Olive!

203
00:11:53,367 --> 00:11:56,000
Let me go!

204
00:11:56,133 --> 00:11:57,467
Maybe she took her
into the woods.

205
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,167
Where the car stopped.

206
00:11:59,300 --> 00:12:00,700
Dan, we have to go back there.

207
00:12:00,833 --> 00:12:01,533
Okay.

208
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,633
Dan, we're going to crash!

209
00:12:22,833 --> 00:12:24,633
Grandmother, are you okay?

210
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:27,433
Grandmother?

211
00:12:30,633 --> 00:12:31,433
Grandmother?

212
00:12:33,233 --> 00:12:34,367
You pest!

213
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,267
You meddlesome pest!

214
00:12:40,333 --> 00:12:42,067
Let me go!

215
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,633
Olive!

216
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:50,133
Hold on to me.

217
00:12:54,833 --> 00:12:56,033
Come on, hold on tight!

218
00:12:59,633 --> 00:13:00,633
Olive!

219
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:28,667
Olive, hold on tight!

220
00:13:56,867 --> 00:13:59,067
What's happening to you?

221
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:00,400
Give her a drink.

222
00:14:00,533 --> 00:14:02,067
- Here's some water.
- Here you go.

223
00:14:06,533 --> 00:14:07,633
What's going on?

224
00:14:11,567 --> 00:14:13,267
I have a bad feeling.

225
00:14:16,267 --> 00:14:17,833
This can't happen!

226
00:14:20,633 --> 00:14:23,067
I have a feeling that something
bad happened.

227
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,367
I don't know exactly.

228
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:27,500
But I'm sure something
bad happened.

229
00:14:27,633 --> 00:14:31,033
We need to go.
We need to follow my children.

230
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:31,967
Kutsy!

231
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:33,733
I'm gonna call a taxi.
Wait here!

232
00:14:33,867 --> 00:14:36,000
Where can I find a taxi?

233
00:14:36,133 --> 00:14:36,667
Taxi?

234
00:14:38,467 --> 00:14:39,233
My God.

235
00:14:41,133 --> 00:14:42,633
Ligaya, Mookie, let's go.

236
00:14:42,767 --> 00:14:43,133
Why?

237
00:14:43,267 --> 00:14:44,633
Come with me.

238
00:14:44,767 --> 00:14:45,333
Where?

239
00:14:45,467 --> 00:14:46,000
Over here.

240
00:14:46,133 --> 00:14:47,233
- Wait.
- What's that?

241
00:14:58,367 --> 00:14:59,067
Emma?

242
00:15:00,533 --> 00:15:02,167
Emma. Are you okay?

243
00:15:05,033 --> 00:15:05,667
Dan,

244
00:15:07,333 --> 00:15:08,233
are you okay?

245
00:15:08,367 --> 00:15:09,333
I'm okay.

246
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,833
Sorry.

247
00:15:11,967 --> 00:15:13,933
- I'm sorry, Emma.
- It's okay.

248
00:15:14,067 --> 00:15:14,633
Sorry.

249
00:15:20,667 --> 00:15:21,967
What?

250
00:15:22,100 --> 00:15:24,467
Let me use your car.
We have to follow Emma.

251
00:15:25,933 --> 00:15:27,233
What? No way!

252
00:15:27,367 --> 00:15:28,533
Oh yeah?

253
00:15:28,667 --> 00:15:30,633
Officers! Officers!

254
00:15:30,767 --> 00:15:33,233
Arrest this woman,
she's Olive Caparas' accomplice!

255
00:15:33,367 --> 00:15:34,767
- Fine! You can have my car!
- Officers!

256
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:37,400
- Here, take it.
- Good, get out of the car!

257
00:15:37,567 --> 00:15:38,567
Get in the car.

258
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,200
- Ligaya, get in.
- Come on, let's go.

259
00:15:43,733 --> 00:15:44,567
Mookie.

260
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:49,200
Mookie, I was forced to do
whatever Olive asked me to do.

261
00:15:49,333 --> 00:15:51,633
It was against my will.

262
00:15:51,767 --> 00:15:53,200
Just shut up.

263
00:15:53,333 --> 00:15:55,033
You talk too much.

264
00:15:55,167 --> 00:15:56,600
Save your excuse later!

265
00:15:56,733 --> 00:15:57,700
Mookie, come on!

266
00:15:57,833 --> 00:15:58,700
Mookie, let's go.

267
00:15:59,733 --> 00:16:00,567
Don't talk to her.

268
00:16:06,333 --> 00:16:08,600
Jade!

269
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:10,500
Jade!

270
00:16:10,633 --> 00:16:11,633
Oh my gosh!

271
00:16:11,767 --> 00:16:12,433
Jade!

272
00:16:13,867 --> 00:16:14,667
Jade!

273
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:18,067
Jade!

274
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:20,233
Jade, are you okay?

275
00:16:20,367 --> 00:16:21,433
Jade?

276
00:16:21,567 --> 00:16:22,967
Jade, no.

277
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:24,700
Jade, wait.

278
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:27,033
Jade!

279
00:16:27,167 --> 00:16:28,033
Olive.

280
00:16:29,300 --> 00:16:30,900
Help me.

281
00:16:32,067 --> 00:16:34,300
Help me, Olive.

282
00:16:34,433 --> 00:16:36,100
Don't worry, Jade.

283
00:16:36,233 --> 00:16:39,333
I'm a doctor, I can help you.
I can save you.

284
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,733
<i> Olive, please.</i>

285
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:47,500
<i>Please, let's talk about this.
As sisters, please.</i>

286
00:16:47,633 --> 00:16:48,567
<i> No!</i>

287
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:51,033
<i>I know that you're going
to take their side!</i>

288
00:16:51,167 --> 00:16:54,000
<i>Because you don't care about me,
Jade!</i>

289
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:58,167
<i>How can you betray
your own sister?</i>

290
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:59,433
<i> I'm sorry.</i>

291
00:16:59,567 --> 00:17:03,267
<i>After all that I've done for you
when you were an junkie!</i>

292
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,533
<i>This is how you're going
to repay me?</i>

293
00:17:05,667 --> 00:17:06,600
<i> No!</i>

294
00:17:06,733 --> 00:17:08,267
<i>Let's see how tough you are now!</i>

295
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:10,433
<i> Come on, fight!</i>

296
00:17:14,967 --> 00:17:16,667
You betrayed me, Jade.

297
00:17:17,867 --> 00:17:18,800
Not just once.

298
00:17:20,833 --> 00:17:23,100
So give me a damn good reason...

299
00:17:24,233 --> 00:17:26,600
Why should I help you now.

300
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:35,867
What do you mean?

301
00:17:37,267 --> 00:17:39,467
We're sisters.

302
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:46,333
You sided with Emma and sent me
to jail.

303
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:50,533
Help me, Olive. Please.

304
00:17:53,333 --> 00:17:53,933
Officers.

305
00:18:06,767 --> 00:18:07,633
Help my wife.

306
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:10,367
Emma.

307
00:18:12,133 --> 00:18:13,833
How are you? Are you hurt?

308
00:18:14,833 --> 00:18:16,100
We're okay.

309
00:18:16,233 --> 00:18:18,067
Did you find Jade and Olive?

310
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,600
We're still looking for them.

311
00:18:19,733 --> 00:18:21,900
We found her getaway vehicle.

312
00:18:22,067 --> 00:18:23,767
We saw that too.

313
00:18:23,900 --> 00:18:28,233
I have a feeling that she took
Jade into the woods.

314
00:18:28,367 --> 00:18:30,300
We have to find Olive.

315
00:18:30,433 --> 00:18:32,000
We can't let her escape.

316
00:18:32,133 --> 00:18:33,967
- Okay. Come with us.
- Here?

317
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:35,200
Let's go, Dan.

318
00:18:50,133 --> 00:18:51,100
Olive, please.

319
00:18:52,567 --> 00:18:54,133
Don't let me die.

320
00:18:55,267 --> 00:18:56,167
Olive.

321
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:59,633
If I help you.

322
00:19:01,867 --> 00:19:03,300
What's in it for me?

323
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:06,500
I'm going back to jail?

324
00:19:07,567 --> 00:19:08,400
No.

325
00:19:09,533 --> 00:19:10,300
No!

326
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:16,967
But I have something else
in mind.

327
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:26,500
You will help me get free, Jade.

328
00:19:28,933 --> 00:19:32,033
So I can take revenge.

329
00:19:35,433 --> 00:19:40,667
And for that to happen,
my dear sister.

330
00:19:43,233 --> 00:19:48,667
You must die.

331
00:20:18,367 --> 00:20:20,667
Thank you for dying, sis.

332
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:31,400
Because of you, I can take
Mookie back from Emma.

333
00:20:45,033 --> 00:20:46,333
From now on,

334
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:05,200
I am Jade Caparas.

335
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:10,633
And you, Olive.

336
00:21:11,767 --> 00:21:14,767
You're dead.

337
00:22:18,767 --> 00:22:21,033
You can look at the remains now.

338
00:22:21,167 --> 00:22:22,400
Mookie.

339
00:22:22,533 --> 00:22:23,833
Sweetie, stay here.

340
00:22:23,967 --> 00:22:24,967
Why?

341
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:27,333
I'm just trying to protect you.

342
00:22:27,467 --> 00:22:28,833
Olive is my daughter.

343
00:22:28,967 --> 00:22:30,167
She's your sister.

344
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:32,433
If you can't accept her
as your sister,

345
00:22:32,567 --> 00:22:34,833
you can at least respect her
as a human being.

346
00:22:34,967 --> 00:22:35,833
She's dead now.

347
00:22:35,967 --> 00:22:37,600
You are not protecting Mookie.

348
00:22:37,733 --> 00:22:40,600
You are taking away her
rights to see the...

349
00:22:40,733 --> 00:22:42,067
The person who tortured her?

350
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:44,133
Dan, she harmed Mookie.

351
00:22:44,267 --> 00:22:47,333
Despite everything she did
to me,

352
00:22:47,467 --> 00:22:49,233
she's still my mom.

353
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:54,033
That's why I want to go
to her wake.

354
00:22:54,167 --> 00:22:56,600
Hi, Jade.

355
00:22:56,733 --> 00:22:59,700
I had been practicing
to be like you.

356
00:22:59,833 --> 00:23:01,133
And look!

357
00:23:01,267 --> 00:23:02,667
I've mastered it!

358
00:23:03,833 --> 00:23:04,767
Olive?
